caption:
&quot;It's Earth Month everyday here at UIC- check out this amazing @uicheritagegarden highlight! 🌻🌎🌈💫

@snleadonclimate recently proudly &quot;...uplifted the incredible climate work of our member institutions like the @thisisuic (UIC) to inspire and encourage all of us to remain committed to fighting the climate crisis.

@uicheritagegarden is more than just a green space, it’s a movement. Rooted in cultural heritage, environmental justice, and hands-on learning, this innovative program empowers students to tackle climate challenges through urban gardening, peer education, and community partnerships. From seed libraries to monarch habitats, student-led initiatives are growing resilience, equity, and climate solutions across campus and beyond.&quot;

🦋 Check out the video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NPNDemTftY8&amp;t=2s

🐜 Read the article here: https://secondnature.org/2025/04/16/promoting-climate-action-through-cultural-heritage-and-environmental-justice/

🍄 To learn more about the Heritage Garden at UIC, visit https://heritagegarden.uic.edu

Video and article written by @sustainableuic.

Congrats UIC Heritage Garden! To many more fruitful seasons! Happy Earth Month 2025! 🐛🌱🐝🌎&quot;.

